JPF - Javeline Platform
========================================

JPF[1] introduces you to writing Rich Internet Applications (RIA's) using Ajax.
Giving you and your users the best of both worlds, your web applications run
in a browser, yet look and feel like compiled desktop applications.
Connecting to external data sources can be done by using Javeline TelePort.

